        public void onRecordReceived​(K key,
                             V value)
        Description copied from interface: StreamingCallback
        This function will be invoked when some records are ready to be consumed. This function could be invoked in parallel when data records arrive at the same time, and if you want to need to do sequential processing, you need to synchronize it in the customized StreamingCallback.onRecordReceived(Object, Object).
